# TransformComposeSystem

## Purpose
Composes the resolved world transform for every entity that has the canonical transform components.
Sole adder and writer of WorldTransformComponent. Reads Position, Rotation, and Scale and writes the
TRS matrix (translate * rotate * scale); reads LocalBounds to compute the render sort key as the
world-space Y of the local bottom-edge (Local Bounds min corner transformed by the world matrix).
Adds WorldTransformComponent (deferred) the first frame an entity has Position/Rotation/Scale, and
writes it in place thereafter.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| PositionComponent | read |
| RotationComponent | read |
| ScaleComponent | read |
| LocalBoundsComponent | read |
| WorldTransformComponent | write |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| WorldTransformComponent | write / add (deferred) | m_Matrix = TRS matrix; m_SortKey = world Y of local bottom edge; added deferred on first appearance |
